        <p>1. The price to be paid by you for any Products will be as quoted via our Site except in cases of obvious error. We are under no obligation to provide the Product to you at the incorrect (lower) price, even after we have sent you an email, if the pricing error is obvious and unmistakeable and could have reasonably been recognised by you as an incorrect pricing.</p>
