        <p>9. If you wish to add to or change your order, or change the date or time of delivery or collection of your order, then we will accommodate you, subject to kitchen space being available to permit us to make your products, provided that you telephone us by 12.00 noon 3 days before your order is due to be collected or delivered.</p>
